<button class="accordion">How does mindfulness affect the brain?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>After practising mindfulness, the grey matter in your brain's amygdala, a region known for its role in stress, can become smaller. The prefrontal cortex is the area of your brain responsible for things like planning, problem-solving, and controlling your emotions.</p>
