<button class="accordion">How does mindfulness help anxiety?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Mindfulness teaches us how to respond to stress with an awareness of what is happening in the present moment, rather than merely acting instinctively, unaware of what emotions or motives may be driving that decision.</p>
</div>
<button class="accordion">Is mindfulness the same as meditation?</button>
